description: This boy was incredibly shy, I could barely get a word out of him. He used to work as a confectioner. A little strange line of work for a guy but I think he liked making cakes. That´s why I offered him a really nice job at the largest cake company in Prague. He loved it, especially for the good salary. I definitely told him about our fee when we talked over the phone but the boy completely forgot about it. The fee took him by surprise, he couldn´t pay it. It was up to me to help the poor guy. I would take care of the fee if he entertained me a little. After some convincing, he undressed and let me have a look. The boy was so lean... I had to touch his innocent body. That´s the nice aspect, you can make people do things if you throw enough cash in their direction.
title: Dirty Scout 154
